{
  "texts": [
    "In traditional fashion design, designers must spend a great deal of time on carefully selecting colors, fabrics, and textures in order to draw a clothing tile image.",
    "Fortunately, computer-aided drawing tools can assist designers in creating clothing templates, which can greatly reduce the workload of designers.",
    "However, clothing design requires a wealth of professional knowledge in practice.",
    "The Metaverse may lower this barrier to fashion design with the help of AI.",
    "It may be that designers and users will be able to specify a few constraints on products in the Metaverse environment, and the system will then instantly generate sketch samples that meet their expectations."
  ]
}